Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一整天就这么白白浪费了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还有两天
